            "title": "Shoka 主题功能展示",
            "date_published": "2024-01-03T06:00:00.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"shoka-主题功能全面展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#shoka-主题功能全面展示\">#</a> Shoka 主题功能全面展示</h1>\n<p>本文展示了 Shoka 主题的各种强大功能。</p>\n<h2 id=\"友链展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#友链展示\">#</a> 🔗 友链展示</h2>\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"item\" title=\"霜月琉璃\" style=\"--block-color:#e9546b;\"><span class=\"exturl image\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9zaG9rYS5sb3N0eXUubWU=\" data-background-image=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/amehime/shoka@latest/images/avatar.jpg\"></span>\n          <div class=\"info\">\n          <span class=\"exturl title\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9zaG9rYS5sb3N0eXUubWU=\">優萌初華</span>\n          <p class=\"desc\">琉璃的医学 & 编程笔记</p>\n          </div></div><div class=\"item\" title=\"Hexo 官网\" style=\"--block-color:#0e83cd;\"><span class=\"exturl image\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlv\" data-background-image=\"/images/404.png\"></span>\n          <div class=\"info\">\n          <span class=\"exturl title\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlv\">Hexo 官网</span>\n          <p class=\"desc\">快速、简洁且高效的博客框架</p>\n          </div></div></div>\n<h2 id=\"代码块展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#代码块展示\">#</a> 💻 代码块展示</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><figcaption><span>高亮示例</span><span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9kZXZlbG9wZXIubW96aWxsYS5vcmcvemgtQ04vZG9jcy9XZWIvSmF2YVNjcmlwdA==\">参考文档 mark:2,5-7</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// JavaScript 函数示例</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"title function_\">greetUser</span>(<span class=\"params\">name</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (!name) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello, Guest!&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">const</span> greeting = <span class=\"string\">`Hello, <span class=\"subst\">$&#123;name&#125;</span>!`</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(greeting);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> greeting;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"title function_\">greetUser</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;张三&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption><span>命令行示例 command:(\"[root@localhost] $\":1,3||\"[user@server] #\":5-6)</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">pwd</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">/home/user/projects</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">ls</span> -la</span><br><span class=\"line\">total 16</span><br><span class=\"line\">drwxr-xr-x 3 user user 4096 Jan  3 14:00 .</span><br><span class=\"line\">drwxr-xr-x 5 user user 4096 Jan  3 13:30 ..</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"练习题展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#练习题展示\">#</a> 🎯 练习题展示</h2>\n<ol>\n<li class=\"quiz true\">\n<p>Hexo 是一个基于 Node.js 的静态博客框架。</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"quiz multi\">\n<p>下列哪些是 Shoka 主题的特色功能？</p>\n<ul class=\"options\">\n<li class=\"correct\">友链展示</li>\n<li class=\"correct\">代码高亮</li>\n<li class=\"correct\">数学公式支持</li>\n<li>视频播放</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<ul class=\"options\">\n<li>✅ 支持友链卡片展示</li>\n<li>✅ 支持多种代码高亮</li>\n<li>✅ 支持 KaTeX 数学公式</li>\n<li>❌ 不是主要特色功能</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li class=\"quiz fill\">\n<p>Shoka 主题基于 <span class=\"gap\">Hexo</span> 框架开发。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"文字特效展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#文字特效展示\">#</a> 🎨 文字特效展示</h2>\n<p>++ 下划线效果 ++<br>\n++ 波浪线效果 ++{.wavy}<br>\n++ 着重点效果 ++{.dot}<br>\n++ 彩色下划线 ++{.primary}<br>\n~~ 删除线效果～～<br>\n== 荧光高亮效果 ==</p>\n<p><span class=\"rainbow\">赤橙黄绿青蓝紫</span><br>\n<span class=\"red\">红色文字</span> <span class=\"blue\">蓝色文字</span> <span class=\"green\">绿色文字</span></p>\n<p>快捷键示例：<span class=\"kbd\">Ctrl</span> + <span class=\"kbd primary\">C</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"隐藏文字展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#隐藏文字展示\">#</a> 🔒 隐藏文字展示</h2>\n<p class=\"blur\">!! 这是隐藏的内容，鼠标悬停显示！！<br>\n!! 这是模糊的内容，选中文字显示！！</p>\n<h2 id=\"️-标签展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#️-标签展示\">#</a> 🏷️ 标签展示</h2>\n<p><span class=\"label\">默认</span> <span class=\"label primary\">主要</span> <span class=\"label info\">信息</span><br>\n<span class=\"label success\">成功</span> <span class=\"label warning\">警告</span> <span class=\"label danger\">危险</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"提醒块展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#提醒块展示\">#</a> 📝 提醒块展示</h2>\n<div class=\"note info 信息提示\">\n<p>这是一个信息提示块，用于显示重要信息。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"note success 成功提示\">\n<p>这是一个成功提示块，表示操作成功完成。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"note warning 警告提示\">\n<p>这是一个警告提示块，提醒用户注意。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"note danger 危险提示\">\n<p>这是一个危险提示块，警告用户潜在风险。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"标签卡展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#标签卡展示\">#</a> 📑 标签卡展示</h2>\n<div class=\"tab\" data-id=\"demo1\" data-title=\"前端技术\">\n<h3 id=\"html\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#html\">#</a> HTML</h3>\n<p>超文本标记语言，用于创建网页结构。</p>\n<h3 id=\"css\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#css\">#</a> CSS</h3>\n<p>层叠样式表，用于网页样式设计。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab\" data-id=\"demo1\" data-title=\"后端技术\">\n<h3 id=\"nodejs\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#nodejs\">#</a> Node.js</h3>\n<p>基于 Chrome V8 引擎的 JavaScript 运行环境。</p>\n<h3 id=\"python\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#python\">#</a> Python</h3>\n<p>简洁优雅的编程语言，适合快速开发。</p>\n</div>\n<h2 id=\"折叠块展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#折叠块展示\">#</a> 📁 折叠块展示</h2>\n<details><summary>primary JavaScript 基础知识</summary><div>\n<p>JavaScript 是一种高级的、解释型的编程语言。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> message = <span class=\"string\">&quot;Hello, World!&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable language_\">console</span>.<span class=\"title function_\">log</span>(message);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div></details>\n<details><summary>success CSS 样式技巧</summary><div>\n<p>CSS 可以让网页变得更加美观。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>使用 Flexbox 布局</li>\n<li>响应式设计</li>\n<li>动画效果</li>\n</ul>\n</div></details>\n<h2 id=\"待办事项展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#待办事项展示\">#</a> ✅ 待办事项展示</h2>\n<ul class=\"task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"cbx_0\" checked=\"true\" disabled=\"true\"><label for=\"cbx_0\"> 学习 Hexo 基础</label></li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"cbx_1\" checked=\"true\" disabled=\"true\"><label for=\"cbx_1\"> 安装 Shoka 主题 {.success}</label></li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"cbx_2\" disabled=\"true\"><label for=\"cbx_2\"> 配置主题功能</label></li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"cbx_3\" disabled=\"true\"><label for=\"cbx_3\"> 编写第一篇文章 {.primary}</label></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"注音展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#注音展示\">#</a> 🔤 注音展示</h2>\n<p><ruby>可<rp>【</rp><rt>か</rt><rp>】</rp>愛<rp>【</rp><rt>わい</rt><rp>】</rp>い<rt></rt>犬<rp>【</rp><rt>いぬ</rt><rp>】</rp></ruby><br>\n<ruby>Hello<rp>【</rp><rt>你好</rt><rp>】</rp></ruby><br>\n<ruby>Hexo<rp>【</rp><rt>静态博客框架</rt><rp>】</rp></ruby></p>\n<h2 id=\"数学公式展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#数学公式展示\">#</a> 🧮 数学公式展示</h2>\n<p>行内公式：<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>m</mi><msup><mi>c</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">E = mc^2</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05764em;\">E</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">m</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">c</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>块级公式：</p>\n\\begin{align}\n\\nabla \\times \\vec{\\mathbf{B}} -\\, \\frac1c\\, \\frac{\\partial\\vec{\\mathbf{E}}}{\\partial t} &= \\frac{4\\pi}{c}\\vec{\\mathbf{j}} \\\\\n\\nabla \\cdot \\vec{\\mathbf{E}} &= 4 \\pi \\rho \\\\\n\\nabla \\times \\vec{\\mathbf{E}}\\, +\\, \\frac1c\\, \\frac{\\partial\\vec{\\mathbf{B}}}{\\partial t} &= \\vec{\\mathbf{0}} \\\\\n\\nabla \\cdot \\vec{\\mathbf{B}} &= 0\n\\end{align}\n\n<h2 id=\"流程图展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#流程图展示\">#</a> 📊 流程图展示</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">graph TD</span><br><span class=\"line\">    A[开始] --&gt; B&#123;是否安装 Hexo?&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    B --&gt;|是| C[安装 Shoka 主题]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    B --&gt;|否| D[安装 Hexo]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    D --&gt; C</span><br><span class=\"line\">    C --&gt; E[配置主题]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    E --&gt; F[编写文章]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    F --&gt; G[部署博客]</span><br><span class=\"line\">    G --&gt; H[完成]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sequenceDiagram</span><br><span class=\"line\">    participant 用户</span><br><span class=\"line\">    participant Hexo</span><br><span class=\"line\">    participant Shoka</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    用户-&gt;&gt;Hexo: 创建新文章</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Hexo-&gt;&gt;Shoka: 应用主题样式</span><br><span class=\"line\">    Shoka-&gt;&gt;用户: 渲染页面</span><br><span class=\"line\">    用户-&gt;&gt;Shoka: 查看效果</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"emoji-展示\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#emoji-展示\">#</a> 😀 Emoji 展示</h2>\n<p>❤️ ⭐️ 🚀 💻 📚 ☕️</p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a class=\"markdownIt-Anchor\" href=\"#总结\">#</a> 总结</h2>\n<p>Shoka 主题提供了丰富的功能，让博客内容更加生动有趣！</p>\n<ul>\n<li>支持多种内容展示方式</li>\n<li>提供丰富的交互功能</li>\n<li>具有优秀的视觉效果</li>\n<li>易于使用和配置</li>\n</ul>\n",
            "tags": [
